imo, artists should do some experiments on each platform to verify how NFT works. There are a lot of questions we have to answer like How to build the business model with NFT? How NFT affect their fans? What's the value of NFT?

(4/n)

.@join_royal created by @3LAU, sells an NFT with the right to receive the percentage of the royalty. 
In terms of the ROI, purchasing royalty NFT does not make sense. But I expect how they are playing out.

(3/n)

What we can get to buy music NFT?

If you buy music NFT on .@soundxyz_  or @catalogworks, you will get the ownership of this song and a source file of the song. And you can sell it on secondary.

(2/n)

How should artists utilize Music NFT?

There are a lot of the music NFT platforms like @soundxyz_ @catalogworks @join_royal @AudiusProject.  Each platforms' vision is slightly different.  #MusicNFT #NFT
